item.title: CVE-2020-5532|2024-08-04T08:30:24.537Z -- extrun%20ltd. -- ilbo%20app
item.description: ilbo App (ilbo App for Android prior to version 1.1.8 and ilbo App for iOS prior to version 1.2.01) allows an attacker on the same network segment to bypass authentication and to view the images which were recorded by the other ilbo user's device via unspecified vectors.
